{"TopicId":91469,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"Rescue Missions with Tier 1 KSC","CreatedByName":"worir4","CreatedById":75980,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-11-28T14:03:09Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"worir4","CreatedById":75980,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-11-28T14:03:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI was just thinking that SQUAD should perhaps remove the rescue missions while the KSC in in the early stages. It would be quite unrealistic to have random Kerbals floating around in space when your agency has just started out. The rescue contracts should only appear in later stages after you have achieved orbit a few times.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWhat do you guys think?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cicatrix","CreatedById":120831,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-11-28T14:06:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EAlthough I would agree it\u0027s non-consistent, still it\u0027s soo much fun. And again - it gives you free Kerbals.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tery215","CreatedById":89094,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-11-28T14:15:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI think that the companies are paying you to rescue \u003Cspan style=\u0022text-decoration:underline;\u0022\u003Etheir\u003C/span\u003E kerbals. They already have the rocket parts (as shown in test contracts) at all times.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EBut, it would be good for players to only get these contracts once they\u0027ve proven they can complete them.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CaptRobau","CreatedById":41695,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-11-28T14:16:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u002B1 as it makes a lot of sense.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LABHOUSE","CreatedById":107761,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-11-28T16:17:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022cicatrix\u0022 data-cite=\u0022cicatrix\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EAlthough I would agree it\u0027s non-consistent, still it\u0027s soo much fun. And again - it gives you free Kerbals.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESince when do kerbals cost money?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"worir4","CreatedById":75980,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-11-28T16:21:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022LABHOUSE\u0022 data-cite=\u0022LABHOUSE\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003ESince when do kerbals cost money?\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EMaybe in the next update they will have an upkeep or something.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cicatrix","CreatedById":120831,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-11-28T16:32:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022LABHOUSE\u0022 data-cite=\u0022LABHOUSE\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003ESince when do kerbals cost money?\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWait, I never actually hired them. They are free?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LABHOUSE","CreatedById":107761,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-11-28T17:27:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022cicatrix\u0022 data-cite=\u0022cicatrix\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EWait, I never actually hired them. They are free?\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_sleep.png\u0022 alt=\u0022-_-\u0022\u003E wow just wow \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_sleep.png\u0022 alt=\u0022-_-\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"worir4","CreatedById":75980,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-11-28T18:38:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022LABHOUSE\u0022 data-cite=\u0022LABHOUSE\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_sleep.png\u0022 alt=\u0022-_-\u